ðŸ”Ž Common Mistakes:
âŒ Not sorting intervals â†’ causes incorrect merges.

âŒ Using merge.size() once and reusing â†’ use merge.size() - 1 inside loop.

âŒ Forgetting Math.max() to update the merged interval's end.

âœ… Quick Tips:
Use Arrays.sort() with lambda for custom sorting.

Always check for overlap using lastEnd < currentStart.

Always test with unsorted input.
